LabelInstructions.DisplayNameEN: The service's product code as a barcode
LabelInstructions.DescriptionEN: 6 characters, contain a technical modulo 103 check digit, not visual. FactCode: 2W. Product code: 4 numbers given by Posti. Bar code type: Licence Plate code 128 a, b and c. The first two characters shall produced in type a or b and the remaining four even numbersin type c. It is not mandatory to use type c, if in the address label is space enough to print out longer bar code. X-value (width of the narrowest bar) 0,42 -0,50 mm (optimal value is 0,46 mm). The minimum resolution in thermal transfer printer is 200 dots / inch. The minimum resolution in laser reproduction is 600 dots / inch. Free space at both sides of the bar code must be at least 5 mm. Minimum height is 20 mm, but when EDI-message is used 12 mm. Use block capitals in bar codes.
